    <title>oh-my-claudecode vs oh-my-openagent：两大 Agent 编排框架深度对比与实用教程</title>
    <link href="https://magicliang.github.io/2026/05/13/oh-my-claudecode-vs-oh-my-openagent-%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%94%A8%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
